ksf-directory project

Builds a tab-delimited text file for printing,
or a specially-delimited text file for use with Microsoft Word's
mail merge.

See the database schema for the students table for the fields to be used in 
the PowerSchool tab-delimited export file that is used to create the
database.  

Create (or re-create) the database use the Rails console to call

Student.import

Once the database has been created, use the Rails console to call

Directory.output_text, or
Directory.output_merge

to write the output files.


